This Job is used by OpenBACH to modify the stat policy of a Job. It moves a configuration file pushed by the Controller in advanced to be the configuration file consider by Rstats then reload Rstats.

Required Arguments:
 job_name :  the name of the Job you want to change the stats policy
 instance_id : the id of the current instance

Statistics: it doesn't produce any statistic

Example:
  - Change the policy of the Job 'rate_monitoring' (currently the instance_id is 5) : -a "job_name rate_monitoring" "instance_id 5"

